high_descs: Turn left to the table.
Pick the knife up.
Turn right twice and head to the sink.
Place the knife inside the cup in the sink.
Grab the cup with the knife in it.
Turn around and head to the table.
Place the cup next to the tomato.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the white table.
Take the knife in front of the tomato on the table.
Turn around, go across the room to the sink.
Put the knife in the glass in the right sink basin.
Take the glass from the sink
Turn around, go back to the white table.
Put the glass on the table between the tomato and the sponge.

high_descs: Move to the table.
Pick up the silver knife on the table.
Bring the knife to the sink.
Put the knife in the glass in the sink.
Pick up the glass in the sink.
Bring the glass to the table.
Put the glass on the table next to the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a glass on the table.
